ouia-safe=\"true\" data-ouia-component-id=\"OUIA-Generated-Title-5\" class=\"pf-c-title pf-m-md task-pflist-title\">Procedure</h6><ol type=\"1\" class=\"pf-c-list task-pflist-list task-pflist-list--proc\"><li class=\"task-pflist-list__item--proc task-pflist-list__item\"><span class=\"task-pflist-list__item__content\"><p>In the <strong>API Designer</strong> designs page of the web console, select the API Designer design that you want to edit.</p> </span></li><li class=\"task-pflist-list__item--proc task-pflist-list__item\"><span class=\"task-pflist-list__item__content\"><p>Click &#8230;&#8203;</p> </span></li></ol></div></div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<div class=\"title\">Verification</div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Is &#8230;&#8203;?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"proc-validating-schema-api-design_getting-started-ad\">Validating an API Designer schema or API design</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph _abstract\">\n<p>You can validate the schema or API content in an API Designer design.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\"><div class=\"title\">Prerequisites</div><div class=\"task-pflist\"><h6 data-ouia-component-type=\"PF4/Title\" data-ouia-safe=\"true\" data-ouia-component-id=\"OUIA-Generated-Title-6\" class=\"pf-c-title pf-m-md task-pflist-title\">Prerequisites</h6><p class=\"task-pflist-subtitle\">In addtion to the prerequisites for this Quick Start, this step requires:</p><ul class=\"pf-c-list task-pflist-list task-pflist-list--prereq\"><li class=\"task-pflist-list__item--prereq task-pflist-list__item\"><span class=\"task-pflist-list__item__content\"><p>You&#8217;ve created, imported, or edited an API Designer design.</p> </span></li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"olist\"><div class=\"title\">Procedure</div><div class=\"task-pflist\"><h6 data-ouia-component-type=\"PF4/Title\" data-ouia-safe=\"true\" data-ouia-component-id=\"OUIA-Generated-Title-7\" class=\"pf-c-title pf-m-md task-pflist-title\">Procedure</h6><